dcterms:description: A heterogeneous MRA dataset consisting of MRA-TOF images acquired from 148 patients, selected from the ICAN database, which includes over 2,500 images from various medical institutions across France.
dcterms:title: ICAN database

dcterms:description: A dataset of Time of Flight (TOF) magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) images used in the study, partitioned into 12 different sets based on the MR devices used for acquisition.
dcterms:title: Time of Flight (TOF) magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset containing bifurcations of interest (BoIs) along the Circle of Willis, used for classification tasks in the study.
dcterms:title: Bifurcations of Interest (BoIs)

dcterms:description: A dataset containing bifurcations of non-interest (BoNI) used in the classification tasks to differentiate between significant and insignificant bifurcations.
dcterms:title: Bifurcations of Non-Interest (BoNI)
